MBOMBELA &#8211; &#8220;Everyone from Mbombela and White River knows Penryn College, they do not know about Penreach. The people of Msholozi know nothing about Penryn, but they all know about Penreach.&#8221;Poonam Dwarkaram, an early childhood develpment (ECD) project coordinator, took Lowvelder on a trip to Msholozi, where ECD is an adventure in making do with what is available.